article.headline: Mississippi 110, Rice 63
article.story:
OXFORD, Miss. (AP) -- Armintie Price scored 23 points and Carla
Bartee added 21 to lead Mississippi to a 110-63 win over Rice on
Saturday.

Ashley Awkward scored 18 for the Lady Rebels, Danetra Forest had
15 points and Ashley Johnson tacked on 11.

Krystal Frasier led Rice with 11 points and Lauren Neaves added
10.

Rice shot just 27 percent from the floor in the first half and
was down 62-32 at halftime.

The Rebels shot 49.4 percent in the game
